QuestData.Title: Insurrection: Waxing Crescent
QuestData.Description: First Arcanist Thalyssra has sent word: there has been communication from Ly'leth. Your help is needed.$b$bJourney to Shal'Aran in Suramar and lend what aid you can.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with First Arcanist Thalyssra in Shal'Aran.
